INSERT INTO `VCs` VALUES ('10','Breakout Ventures','breakoutventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1488437682/rjihaylzmtpzh2dzbjrx.png','Breakout Ventures is a new, early stage fund that backs bold scientist entrepreneurs working at the intersections of technology, biology, materials, and energy.','https://www.breakout.vc/','2417163674a945c2dc216b43630e776e','Bldg C, Suite 400','San Francisco','94129','CA'),('100','CTW Venture Partners','ctw-venture-part','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470390545/uct4damdzljidea3w1w2.png','CTW was founded in 2009 by Palaniswamy “Raj” Rajan to invest in and assist early-stage entrepreneurs in the southeastern United States who are engaged in disruptive innovations and technologies. The partnership represents nearly 35 deals and more than 15 years of investing. CTW is based in Atlanta, GA.','http://www.ctwvp.com/','2babc8a50d2c62b7c40f8a64cbc5bcc9','200','Dunwoody','30338','GA'),('101','Lariat Partners','lariat-partn','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470724666/dckvlpnaaq1vzannefjl.png','Lariat Partners is a private equity firm specializing in consolidations, management buyouts, recapitalizations, buy and build in fragmented industries, and growth capital investments in lower middle market companies. The firm seeks to invest in consumables, specialty agriculture, energy, environmental services, and healthcare services. It seeks to invest in companies with EBITDA between $2 million and $20 million. The firm seeks to invest in recurring revenue businesses with a strong preference for entrepreneur-managed companies.','http://lariatpartners.net/','2fb643f08e4d203922ac942acb3431f6',NULL,'Denver',NULL,'CO'),('102','Root Ventures','rootvc','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470890932/mdowwlhvb3frrcaqnhyu.png','Root Ventures is a venture capital firm that offers investment services for companies utilizing hardware, development tools, and data science. It was founded in 2013 by Avidan Ross and is based in California.','http://www.root.vc/','31fcde60bd9535a13256114d1eaf1c09',NULL,'San Francisco','94110','CA'),('103','High Alpha','high-alpha-llc','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470642206/nwlbynanfol21kgptdap.png','High Alpha, based in Indianapolis, Indiana, is comprised of High Alpha Studio and High Alpha Seed. High Alpha Studio conceives, launches and scales next generation enterprise by providing a blend of services including: product development, sales and marketing, finance, brand and design, and talent development. High Alpha Seed invests in High Alpha Studio companies and other emerging enterprise cloud companies. The combination of High Alpha Studio and High Alpha Seed represents a new model for entrepreneurship that seeks to help companies reduce friction, increase velocity, and achieve enterprise scale.','http://highalpha.com/','3339ae177fd20900247f7ddb2f4d10ff',NULL,'Indianapolis','46204','IN'),('104','Mount Wilson Ventures','mount-wilson-ventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472186600/k8r5sgpow8ltazkyoawg.png','Mount Wilson Ventures specializes in building early-stage startups, especially those based in the hard-sciences; advising industrial partners; and, developing innovation communities.','http://www.mountwilsonvc.com/','3365ccf0bd6759cd4c349a500be1e734',NULL,'Pasadena','91103','CA'),('105','RainmakeMe','rainmakeme','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1471545562/auo5l74muqcpv4tz1lsb.png','If you are an entrepreneur and don’t have the bootstrap, friends and family or are trying to access mainstream capital to launch your business then you have found your suitor.\r\n\r\nSimply send us your Application for funding, we will review, follow up with you directly and if your idea is accepted we will invest $25,000 to $50,000.  Use the money to pay for your website, mobile application, marketing initiatives, to obtain a patent, to find a partner, to obtain your proof of concept, pay for legal work, to develop a prototype so you can apply to the hundreds of crowdfunding and accelerator businesses to reach your next stage. \r\n\r\nWhat\'s important is you remain in control while we act as a partner and advisor as much or as little as you need. Think of RainmakeMe as your one on one accelerator program. One on one is correct. We do not take part in the Lotto Strategy so many programs pursue today. We are an active lead investor that doesn\'t only come with a check. We work for our negotiated share and get your company operationally institutionalized so you can grow.\r\n\r\nWorried about your idea being stolen? Sign our Confidentiality Agreement and we will countersign and send it back to you before you submit. \r\n\r\nTo learn more about RainmakeMe please take a few minutes to navigate our site as well as the social media links below.','http://rainmakeme.com/','34bdddf93c789b8b0c61c2f7d9b47719',NULL,'New York',NULL,'NY'),('107','Pontifax AgTech','pontifaxagtech','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470113803/bcxkbsbuzuz40kiju6ii.png','Pontifax Global Food and Agriculture Technology Fund (\"Pontifax AgTech\") is a pioneering growth capital investor in food and agriculture technology. We invest globally in growing businesses that improve agricultural productivity, nutrition, health, sustainability and supply chain efficiency.','http://www.pontifaxagtech.com','3d650601f52fe502b64c96d161ef8b7b',NULL,'Santa Monica','90404','CA'),('108','Homestead Partners','homesteadpartners','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1469933399/xavgqh0c5dyfeub0uxhq.png','The investment vehicle through which Chris and Stephanie Herndon make modest investments into early stage companies and real estate projects. In addition to writing small checks, Homestead also provides domain expertise and intros, when helpful.','http://www.homesteadpartners.co','3f5d9511a1ead37ebce7b537f5b734fe',NULL,'San Francisco',NULL,'CA'),('109','BrandProject','brand-project','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472244782/so1haroomzx1yfxtoeu5.png','BrandProject rapidly scales early-stage consumer businesses with Founders.\r\n\r\nWe take a strategic approach to building solid foundations, focusing on key business building pillars, and providing the financial and operational resources to succeed.\r\n\r\nOur team has a wealth of experience building some of the world’s leading consumer products and technology companies. Collectively, the partners have launched over 100 new products and services for global icons including Nike, LEGO, Starbucks, Virgin, Diageo, Cadbury-Schweppes, and Colgate-Palmolive.\r\n\r\nWe have invested and helped build innovative new brands including Daily Harvest, FRESHLY, Owlet, Ritual Co., Chefs Plate, Awake Chocolate, Rumble Supershake, The Coveteur, Surf Easy, Hello Products and BRIKA.\r\n\r\nBrandProject is actively looking to back passionate entrepreneurs who are creating differentiated products for large markets. Entrepreneurs can get in touch at ideas@brandproject.com. For more information, get in touch at info@brandproject.com.','http://www.brandproject.com/','42214538581ecd5fc0ea05b2731343e6','110 East 25th Street','New York','10010','NY'),('11','Portage Venture Partners','portage-venture-partners-2',NULL,'Portage Venture Partners is a venture capital firm specializing in investments in seed and early stage companies. It primarily invests in information technology and life sciences businesses with a focus on Internet, telecommunications, business and IT services, software and hardware, nanotechnology, medical devices, biotechnology, and healthcare services.',NULL,'2ad13df009f24ce1012978ec80395c4e',NULL,'Northfield',NULL,'MN'),('110','Sandy Hill Ventures','sandy-hill-ventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470080025/fggzmsyaj33g0xfw7oeo.png',NULL,'http://www.sandyhillventures.com','451544bad61febff5347ea5327d43fc9',NULL,'San Francisco','94118','CA'),('111','CNI Ventures','cniventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470052964/xwyb1a3rq8nx226exjcw.png',NULL,NULL,'475d126db94b5a157a76f5e905da3ec6',NULL,'Phoenix','85004','AZ'),('112','Zephyr Management','zephyrmanagement','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472633337/mrid4aycb8o5zuvburur.png','Since 1994, they have sponsored 22 funds with approximately $1.2 billion in committed capital which are managed from their offices in New York, London and Bangalore.\r\n\r\nWith a global network of partners, Zephyr is positioned to identify sustainable secular growth changes which lead to attractive investment opportunities for their investors.\r\n\r\nWhile their focus is on the creation and execution of innovative investment strategies, the operating style is conservative and sustainable.\r\n\r\nManagers strictly adhere to their respective mandates and investments are selected based on rigorous fundamental research. Today, Zephyr manages investment funds in India and Sri Lanka, and they are actively researching new investment opportunities around the world.','http://www.zmlp.com/','49cfb0bb71e1e0056476d5a54ace5851',NULL,'New York','10022','NY'),('113','Lurkin™','lurkin-vc','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1474695211/fifitbnokfsmlatf6nyb.png','Lurkin is a diversified venture company.','http://Lurkin.com','4ceb957c46453244a2ee0a491d60c9d1',NULL,'Los Angeles','90014','CA'),('114','PTB Ventures','ptb','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1490118758/owkap2a7ep2zp4q3ionf.jpg','PTB is a thesis driven venture capital firm investing in early-stage companies in the digital identity ecosystem.','http://www.ptbvc.com','534fe0a2a8d0795e53027cb111bed61c',NULL,'New York',NULL,'NY'),('115','Lakeland Ventures Development','lakeland-venture','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472552657/gjnq7ripcyz6fjm2pbwd.png','Lakeland Ventures is committed to providing resources to entrepreneurs developing innovative technologies and commercially scalable business ideas that help people live safer and healthier lives.\r\n\r\nWorking both independently and with our strategic investment partners, we strive to provide our businesses with much more than just investment capital. We combine our business development expertise and extensive resource network with our passion for impact entrepreneurship to ensure the best possible chance for success.','http://www.lakelandventuresdevelopment.com/','554140f5ec033b344fb289b74b47cf0b',NULL,'Grosse Pointe','48230','MI'),('116','Technicolor Ventures','technicolorventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1469883160/ccbxkz8efdwjjdz3a8w2.png','Technicolor Ventures is a stage agnostic venture group, exploring the future of content and business technologies/applications.','http://www.technicolor.vc','56d65a940cdc9ec96b01563405fd9f9b',NULL,'Los Angeles',NULL,'CA'),('117','Armory Square Ventures','armorysquare-ventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1487933457/flfmph62xdybbk6ruwpu.png','Armory Square Ventures is a venture fund based in Upstate New York and NYC.  They often provide the first round of institutional capital for companies targeting the largest industries across New York State. They are actively involved in all aspects of company growth from recruiting senior talent, customers, and co-investors to providing general support.','http://www.armorysv.com','583aae932ffdd9943cfa7638549eeac5','2nd Floor','Syracuse','13202','NY'),('118','Ottoman Ventures','ottoman-vc','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470743603/cqu29fiqseujibkqejyx.png','Ottoman Ventures is a venture capital enabler and management consultancy company based in Palo Alto, CA with offices in Istanbul, Turkey. Its aim is to collect, evaluate, filter and invest in the leading innovative ideas generated in Turkey and beyond.\r\n\r\nTurkey provides a great opportunity for venture capital investors looking for diversification and new opportunities in a big market. Both the world-wide economic crisis and the “almost-non-existent” venture capital investment practices in Turkey provide an opportunity gap for all the investors interested in venture capital investments in the region.','http://www.ottomanventures.com/','5f788f6206179f890ea38d14c6a4d08f',NULL,'Palo Alto',NULL,'CA'),('119','Aspire Ventures','aspireventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470223055/h0xglfjnb5vxuv2vr2si.png','Aspire Ventures is a private equity firm focused on impact investment and disruptive B2B2C technologies. We leverage our capital, intellectual property and domain expertise in the Internet of Things (IoT) to help solve today’s biggest problems.\r\n\r\nOur investment thesis is simple - if our portfolio companies don\'t have to reinvent the wheel they can accomplish much more, far faster, and at far lower R&D cost. Not reinventing the wheel means we\'ve built (in-house) the top-notch know-how and intellectual property in IoT-related technologies for our portfolio companies to leverage - encompassing industry leading technologies in the areas of mobile, cloud, machine learning, and big data analytics.\r\n\r\nOur rapidly growing team includes over 70 of the best engineers and scientists in their fields. Our technical staff includes over 20 machine learning and predictive analytics experts who have been leaders everywhere from the Russian space program to the back-offices of the Fortune 500 - and who possess advanced degrees from the best research universities in the field. Our full-time entrepreneurs-in-residence work exclusively on behalf of Aspire portfolio companies and boasts a broad array of renowned innovators in fields like cloud computing, mobile health, mobile payments, wearables, solar tech, medical imaging, media, and artificial intelligence.\r\n\r\nFor our early stage companies, Aspire further provides all the resource a company needs in order to have a realistic shot at transforming its target industry including capital, IP and legal services, world class lab and work space, accounting, marketing and administrative services.\r\n\r\nThrough our venture investments we are dedicated to making an impact and being the very best at delivering value through the Internet of Things. We are bringing breakthrough technologies to market faster and more cost effectively for the benefit of people worldwide, and we hope you will join our growing community of investors, business partners, industry experts, innovators, scientists and strategists to become part of something really powerful— An Aspire Company.\r\n\r\nASPIRE VENTURES COMPANY PORTFOLIO\r\n\r\nappMobi\r\nDisfa\r\nInfinistat\r\nMedStatix\r\nPowch\r\nTempo Health\r\nVitaVista\r\nWhite Sparrow\r\nWylei','http://www.aspirevc.com','62c1f233a50482b7235f5a199ced431a',NULL,'Lancaster','17603','PA'),('12','Green Bay Ventures','green-bay-ventures','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1481509412/ivu8mp7xadiowzhzll2s.png',NULL,'http://www.greenbayventures.com','2e9c7b720ecf36e5adbdb8b7dfcf3117','Suite 200','San Francisco','94133','CA'),('120','Maryland Angels Council','maryland-angelscouncil',NULL,'A venture capital firm specializing in growth capital, early stage, and seed capital. It primarily invests in new media, e-commerce, telecom, software, Internet, bioscience, biotech, information technology, or health markets. The firm typically invests in companies based in Maryland and the Mid-Atlantic region. It will co-invest with established venture capital firms or other investment vehicles.',NULL,'66e272f11655e047cbc88e9c45baaded',NULL,'Glenwood','21738','MD'),('121','Coniston Capital','coniston-capital','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1471983110/q7ysofb048z4jiyegpew.png','Coniston Capital is the investment management vehicle of Rick Patterson.  He is a Director of Global Weather Corporation and RedShelf, Inc.\r\n\r\nConiston Capital seeks investment opportunities in compelling small media, entertainment and business service companies located in the United States.','http://www.coniston-capital.com/','6c407b6aed1981cf646c82d3b6f93c0c',NULL,'Chatham',NULL,'NJ'),('122','Unshackled Ventures','unshackled-ventur','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470902887/kw3dsmzg8gql7vamx6ya.png','Unshackled is an early stage venture capital fund created in 2014 to support foreign-born entrepreneurs as they turn their innovative ideas into reality. Founded by two friends who understood the challenges facing immigrants, Unshackled helps these innovators turn their idea into the next great American company. By providing a rich environment to research and develop their concepts from idea to funded and staffed company, Unshackled gives diverse entrepreneurs the opportunity to innovate and tackle some of the U.S.’s biggest problems, ultimately improving the way we all live and work. \r\n\r\nUnshackled is supported by 80+ highly influential investors, including Brad Feld, First Round Capital, Jerry Yang and Laurene Powell Jobs. The fund has made more than a dozen investments in nearly 30 founders born in 6 different continents.','http://unshackledvc.com/','70c8257354014fa9d2f053652c7a2d74',NULL,'Palo Alto','94301','CA'),('123','Accelerant','accelerant-venture-capital-fund','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472278065/bvh8i1hcvf4pjiwu5cxc.png',NULL,'http://www.accelerantdayton.com','76343b667920ec33d4d626e28186cd64',NULL,'Dayton','45423','OH'),('124','Shamrock Ventures, B.V.','shamrock-ventures-b-v','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470820358/j0apqlyuhxaxdhkseclm.png',NULL,NULL,'76a0d24e9ca66048113ab0082bd9cd6e',NULL,'Cambridge','02142','MA'),('125','Bedford Funding Capital','bedford-funding-capital','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1491804468/wvs6cyco8mxratmq0b04.png','Bedford Funding is a private equity firm providing long-term capital to businesses in the consolidating and fragmented technology industry with experienced industry focus in the software and IT services sectors. There extensive operating backgrounds have led to a keen understanding of the opportunities inherent in technology enterprises. Bedford Funding makes investments worldwide from its headquarters located in White Plains, New York.','http://www.bedfordfunding.com/','7b50057e0370b654f8e7454f3a9cd844',NULL,'White Plains',NULL,'NY'),('126','ASU Venture Devils','asu-venture-devils','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472001219/wig3tmuwq86eat3cn3hq.png',NULL,NULL,'7bc19f14f15c922a64b1b490567b3962','Arizona State University, P.O. Box 9309','Tempe','85287-9309','AZ'),('127','Bedrock Capital Partners','bedrockcapital-partners','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1469947397/fpxem8tidaqwmavb6wpf.png','Bedrock Capital Partners is a venture capital firm that specializes in early stage investments. It seeks to invest in healthcare and information technology sectors. The firm achieves liquidity through an initial public offering, merger, or sale. The offices of the company are located across the North America.\n\nBedrock Capital Partners is a U.S.-based company that was founded in 1987.','http://www.bedrockcapital.com/','801c4922534bde886ef845de52ddabb9',NULL,'San Francisco','94111','CA'),('128','Figtree Partners','figtree-part',NULL,NULL,'http://www.figtreepartners.com/','8267a9783b190afd65f7710fc76c8fc2','13th Floor','San Francisco','94111','CA'),('129','Venture for America','venture-foramerica','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470910154/zew6mb11zxegcgqcs16y.png','Venture for America is an organization that prepares college graduates for careers in the startup community.  Their mission is to revitalize American cities and communities through entrepreneurship, to enable their best and brightest to create new opportunities for themselves and others, and to restore the culture of achievement to include value-creation, risk and reward, and the common good.','http://ventureforamerica.org/','84a05f3d1746f05bddb625d1c070d7ef',NULL,'New York','10001','NY'),('13','Gateway','gatewayincubator','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1484715136/jljfu1sxsokkjib08w4b.