ies to propel your business to a new level of success.\r\n\r\n-Fresh Perspective: Look at your business from a different angle and design a turnaround plan that defies conventional wisdom. \r\n\r\n-Don’t run away from Challenges: Identify creative ways to attack the company’s existing markets as well as find new markets. \r\n\r\n-Family is our core: A strong family is built around everyone looking out for each other. We only work on deals that are a win/win for all stakeholders.','http://karmelcapital.com/','a4122ff45be580eeef8f519f053a059e',NULL,'Vista','92081','CA'),('137','J.W. Childs Associates','j-w-childs-associates1','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1470661001/kdbixemfejsurmfmfuhr.png','Boston-based J.W. Childs Associates is an established private equity firm specializing in leveraged buyouts and recapitalizations of middle-market growth companies. With a focus on consumer products, specialty retail, and healthcare services businesses, we make control investments in growth companies or companies that have the potential for growth with the help of our operating and managerial partners. Our investment and operating professionals have decades of private equity and executive management experience, and we employ a consistent, disciplined investment strategy that has produced strong returns throughout our history and across numerous economic and credit cycles. Since our founding in 1995, we have invested approximately $3 billion of equity capital in more than 40 businesses with an aggregate enterprise value at the time of investment of over $12 billion.  We are currently seeking new investment opportunities for our 2014 vintage fourth fund.','http://www.jwchilds.com/','a5d279621d8c8ada035fa54372da2187',NULL,'Waltham','02451','MA'),('138','DWP Investments','dwp-investments','http://public.crunchbase.com/t_api_images/v1472572943/qwzythugw8rjaehjiiqh.jpg',NULL,NULL,'a61e7b0529cda41793ac583897a95d5f',NULL,'Scottsdale','85251','AZ'),('139','SV FRONTIER','sv-f